Why Learn CLI

- Our development tooling runs on CLI i.e. npm, nvm, pip, gradle, etc.
- Faster Navigation
- More Freedom/control (be responsible)
- ability to run or access servers

ASSUMPTIONS
- WSL is installed and using CLI in WSL workspace (Window Users)
- Git is installed


ls === show different files in the current directory.
ls -a === This will show hidden files.
ls -a -l === long list of files and hidden files.
man (command) === to show details about the command